subject: Out of Office - Returning 4/21 RE: OR - Eugene PD Phase 1 + Flock Safety
body:
[EXTERNAL ?]

Hello,

Thank you for your email. I am currently out of the office and will not be able to respond to emails during this time. I will return on Monday, April 21st and address your message as soon as possible after my return.

If you would like to see a status of cameras, please check here: Deployment Tracker [link https://urldefense.com/v3/__https://planner.flocksafety.com/planning-portal/deployment-tracker__;!!AHBTabvNIkIbFg!hya6QFXhbMEE8YfJzeL13D3WA-UGb4gHdkuYO6KDglhGxMRzBdrD8AtVKMBcHkrnmTMRdCFi-nY1o3QnJMYsWaRnaRVV0sd9ZQ$ ].

Thank you for your understanding, and I will be in touch!



-- 

	
 
Matt Triana
Project Manager
